As high-end smartphones continue to improve their features, their prices continue on an upward trajectory. Flagship smartphones from leading brands can now cost upwards of R30,000 – a figure that many South Africans are unwilling to pay. This is why manufacturers are bringing out mid-range smartphones that offer great features for a more reasonable price tag. These smartphones offer users powerful performance, elegant design, and impressive features – all for a price that is significantly lower than premium alternatives. We compared some of the best mid-range smartphones in South Africa, which should give prospective smartphone buyers a good idea of the value a mid-range smartphone can offer. Pricing was taken from Takealot.       